				<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="544">
					<tr valign="top">
						<td width="10" class="o">*</td>
						<td class="o">Ginseng is a food with excellent physiological effect. Saponin reduces blood glucose level. As medicinal herb, it has anti-cancer effects and improves immune functions.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="20" border="0"></td></tr>
